data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch-style home nestled in a serene rural setting in Bethel Township. This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm. The living room is a cozy haven, centered around a gas log fireplace with a stunning full-wall stone hearth, creating a warm and inviting ambiance for gatherings with family and friends. The heart of the home is an updated kitchen boasting a stylish tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a layout that seamlessly combines form and function. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated, ensuring a touch of luxury in your daily routine. The huge primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en suite bathroom with both a soaking tub and a shower, dual vanities, and a generously sized closet. Downstairs you will find an expansive finished basement, where a huge rec room and a wood burning fireplace await, ready to accommodate your favorite activities and hobbies. Step outside to discover a large patio perfect for entertaining and a fenced backyard offering privacy and space for outdoor activities. The backyard is irrigated and there is also a 10' x 16' shed for lawn equipment and additional storage. The 3-car garage and oversized driveway provide ample parking and storage options. This residence offers the best of both worlds--tranquil rural living with the convenience of a short drive to Huber Heights' city amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home--a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality awaits.
